= Series Opening/Point Release/Series Closing Checklist =

The official checklists for the kernel team is in the relevant proceedure
files this directory.  Each proceedure file represents a separate
checklist.  Each section represents a list to create and populate.
Within each section each top level list item represents a separate card
in that checklist.

Create a new jira EPIC on the Proceedures board in the KERN project.  The
proceedure-cards script will use the jira API create the issues from the
proceedure file:

  ./proceedure-cards [--component <component>] [--epic-key <epic-key>] <project> <proceedure.yaml>

  ./proceedure-cards --component SPOC --epic-key KERN-3021 KERN series-opening.yaml
